title: Bobby Asks Matthew McConaughey About His 'Dallas Buyer’s Club' Diet + Brothers Osborne Reacts To ACM Nominations + Bobby Feud: Favorite 90’s TV Shows!
itunes:title: Bobby Asks Matthew McConaughey About His 'Dallas Buyer’s Club' Diet + Brothers Osborne Reacts To ACM Nominations + Bobby Feud: Favorite 90’s TV Shows!
description:
We talked to Matthew McConaughey about his benefit concert last night, how he lost 50 pounds for Dallas Buyers club and if he ever has to audition for roles anymore. We talk to Brothers Osborne about TJ’s friendship with Kacey Musgraves and how John reacted to their ACM nominations. We play a round of the Bobby Feud with the top 10 TV shows from the 90s.
